questions.question:
你会如何为 `Clients` 实现一个可用的 `Append()` 方法？
```go
package main
type Client struct {
  Name string
}
type Clients struct {
  clients []*Client
}
func main() {
  c:= &Clients{clients.make([]*Client,0)}
  c.Append(&Client{Name: "LinkedIn API})
}
```

questions.explanation:
```go
func (cc *Clients) Append(c *Client) {
cc.clients = append(cc.clients, c)
}
```
```go
func (cc *Clients) Append(c *Client) {
cc.append(c)
}
```
```go
func (cc Clients) Append(c Client) {
cc.clients = append(cc.clients, c)
}
```
```go
func (cc *Clients) Append(c Client) {
cc.clients.append(c)
}
```

